            \ grep:%::FIXME\|TODO\|NOTE\|XXX\|COMBAK\|@todo<CR>
" outlines (also ctags)
nnoremap <silent><Leader>t :Unite -silent -vertical -winwidth=40
            \ -direction=topleft -toggle outline<CR>
" junk files
  nnoremap <silent><Leader>d :Unite -silent junkfile/new junkfile<CR>

